text: Nahid is the Persian name for the Iranian goddess Anahita. Nahid can be *Nahid (movie), 2015 Iranian film *Nahid (magazine), Ottoman magazine *Nahid-1, Iranian satellite ==People with the given name== *Nahid Kiani (born 1998), is an Iranian taekwondo practitioner. *Nahid Islam (born 1998), is a Bangladeshi student activist.
title: Nahid
